novation changes the shop’s appearance, giving you more control over how your space looks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149100/extras/c9368880d9b4fd094825076ff1a5e3c6.poster.avif?t=1770386899\" width=1170 height=566 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149100/extras/c9368880d9b4fd094825076ff1a5e3c6.webm?t=1770386899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149100/extras/c9368880d9b4fd094825076ff1a5e3c6.mp4?t=1770386899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149100/extras/09ac704db44686d288ca861f433f58b9.avif?t=1770386899\" width=950 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your old pawn shop to unlock new possibilities. Expand available space, improve shop functionality, and prepare your business for bigger deals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase product licenses to unlock new item categories and gain access to more valuable goods as your pawn empire grows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149100/extras/345e452ba1c0a9c8526e5b6bc4213069.poster.avif?t=1770386899\" width=1170 height=566 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149100/extras/345e452ba1c0a9c8526e5b6bc4213069.webm?t=1770386899\" type=\"video/webm; code